<P><HI>CHild&punc; How Old art thou&punc;</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Child,</SPEAKER>
<P>I am told, Fa-ther, that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> am be-tween three and fou<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> years Old.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Can&s;t thou tell who was the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">irst Man God made?</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Ch.</SPEAKER>
<P>Yes, <HI>A-dam</HI> was the fi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">an.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Who was it that kill-ed&punc; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Bro-ther?</HI></P>
