<P><HI>Who did walk wiu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> three hun-dred years, and was <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> fla<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ed that he &s;hould not &s;ee</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"></P>
</SP>
