<SPEAKER>Ch.</SPEAKER>
<P>E-n<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">h.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fa.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Who was the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> that e-verli-ved?</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Ch.</SPEAKER>
<P>Ma-thu-<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></P>
