<P><HI>Who built the A<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">k, and w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> on-ly Righ-te-ous in his Day?</HI></P>
